{"tid":612652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中藥炒到一半大爆炸　目擊者：庸醫加錯藥","createTime":"2018-04-01T04:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T04:46:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc868770121a8c748816cd24f47ebefde15c6c1b","tid":612652,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180401/640_e791621aa64cd2659b8a35a37122edb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180401%2F640_e791621aa64cd2659b8a35a37122edb6.jpg&h=3cf32d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國廣西柳州市一個路邊攤周五（30日）發生爆炸，造成60多歲的老闆林姓男子，及5名老人被燒傷。目擊者表示，林男是一名「遊醫」（四海行醫的人），當時正在炒中藥，打算炒好後把藥粉敷到患者身上，沒想到炒到一半就爆炸了。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者覃姓女子表示，林男當時在草藥攤內，用酒精燈炒藥，由於病人不斷催促，慌忙間拿了一瓶液體倒進鍋內，「肯定是酒精，一倒就爆（炸）了」。5名在草藥攤內敷藥治療的老人，因為走避不及，頭部、手部、腿部被燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n林男向警方供稱，自己是一名「遊醫」，他為病人敷藥前，會在對方身上塗抹酒精，然後用酒精燈炒草藥後，會把藥敷到患者身上。當天想這樣做時，酒精燈的火不慎點燃患者，後來酒精燈就爆炸燃燒。由於警方發現，林沒有醫師執照，已把他帶回調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180401/1326415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180401%2F1326415&d=4F49BeM%2Fj3GDFsAwdGZ%2BfTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=406d9034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180401%2F1326415&h=6ec91fda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180401/1326415</a>"},{"pid":"e3c7a74daa0c2096bc56ea3a66a9f642b4f5b8d1","tid":612652,"uid":89037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1b24aba4d953b232e18fd7f43b42dd52788883","tid":612652,"uid":45847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"煉金術士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d355865b3c65b67a256a5d60d19c090eedb9e5","tid":612652,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"落錯炸藥？"},{"pid":"b80d539417f422bee8f2aefc5b4aa57620db0e33","tid":612652,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/e41d70940cd6e9a1b46951c4120f4c34/tenor.gif?itemid=5464737\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2Fe41d70940cd6e9a1b46951c4120f4c34%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D5464737&h=d1df80ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02d977b002d3496dd3c60575cb13c67e9437dcf6","tid":612652,"uid":65406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"火藥<del>發明</del>(發現)國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38af0c305c2887f33ad1643383d4112c19a80bd3","tid":612652,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98d355865b3c65b67a256a5d60d19c090eedb9e5","tid":612652,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"落錯炸藥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T04:46:50.000Z","msg":"知唔知炸藥點黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}